				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>y- epes getun, hot zi opgeshnitn &lt;di&gt; bisele hor. ikh hob gemeynt ikh vel mikh hargenen UNK, vos zi geyt mir shoyn vider aropshnaydn di hor.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
