				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>zog ikh "vos hob ikh getun? &lt;zi hot&gt; dokh nisht gevolt mayn mame lozn zitsn, hob ikh &lt;zi gegebn&gt; a khap far di hor. ikh </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
