				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>oy, JA, zikher, shoyn hobn a shtikl broyt tsu UNK esn. eyner hot zi gezogt "oy, ikh hob, ikh UNK &lt;eyer&gt; shpayz"</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
